attributes.title: ✨🍪horrible💞app🧚🏼🐻
attributes.review: The app took about nine months to download. Also when I first opened it there was a horrible horrible orange Oompa Loompa staring at me. I did not know what to think. I thought I was going to be murdered. And then all of my apps got deleted.My phone was wiped clean from everything. I’d prefer to have my phone back. And I don’t like orange Oompa Loompa’s well some of them but not this one.

attributes.title: God awful
attributes.review: Me the whole hearted republican was white male that I am I decided to download this app to keep up with our leader 😁 But.... it was awful, GOD AWFUL. I would try to inform and educate myself with what he’s doing to win the election this year, and my phone would almost be like it’s own person if you will 😂 it would take me out of the app and make my phone go crazy! Such as opening the message app and typing gibberish, taking multiple random pictures, and more all by itself!! I almost had to get a new phone because of this monstrosity. When the app didn’t do this however, the facts that were stated about the 2020 election, trump campaign, etc. we’re all FALSE! The facts made no sense what so ever and said that trump was a barb? What the f$#¥ is a barb?? Anyways I inform you TO NOT DOWNLOAD THIS APP. It is a waste of time and is completely unprofessional especially coming from our president...

attributes.title: it’s the 🍊 for me
attributes.review:
Good morning, I decided to download this app because I was curious about Bunker Boy’s plans. I was immediately dissatisfied upon launching to see the grotesque image of a wrinkly racist 🍊?? I would recommend changing the image to something more pleasant to look at

MORE LIKE FAKE NEWS!!!!!
